member.name: M:Jellyfin.LiveTv.TunerHosts.HdHomerun.LegacyHdHomerunChannelCommands.ChannelAndProgramRegex
member.remarks:
Pattern:
\\/ch([0-9]+)-?([0-9]*)
Explanation:
○ Match the string "/ch".
○ 1st capture group.
○ Match a character in the set [0-9] greedily at least once.
○ Match '-' atomically, optionally.
○ 2nd capture group.
○ Match a character in the set [0-9] atomically any number of times.

member.name: M:Jellyfin.LiveTv.TunerHosts.M3uParser.KeyValueRegex
member.remarks:
Pattern:
([a-z0-9\\-_]+)=\\"([^"]+)\\"
Options:
RegexOptions.IgnoreCase
Explanation:
○ 1st capture group.
○ Match a character in the set [-0-9A-Z_a-z\u0130\u212A] atomically at least once.
○ Match the string "=\"".
○ 2nd capture group.
○ Match a character other than '"' atomically at least once.
○ Match '"'.
